   <head>Ancient and modern languages</head>
    <p>Text in a language other than the default language of the document should be indicated by the
        use of the attribute @lang='' with the ISO 639 three-letter code for the language in
        question. In addition, the code must be declared in the <tag>teiHeader</tag> (see 5.3.3
        Using <tag>profileDesc</tag>) in TEI.2/teiHeader/profileDesc/langUsage.</p>
